# PO files (development)

- **Headers:** Use Ukrainian language and plural rules:
  - `Language: uk`
  - Ukrainian plural formula: `nplurals=3; plural=(n%10==1 && n%100!=11 ? 0 : n%10>=2 && n%10<=4 && (n%100<10 || n%100>=20) ? 1 : 2);`
- **Translations:** Keep `msgstr` values in English so devs can read them during development.
